<emphasis box="[322,774,1339,1361]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="35">Rhipidia (Eurhipidia) formosana formosana</emphasis>
Alexander, 1923
</taxonomicName>
. 5: Hypopygium, lateral view; 6: Hypopygium, dorsal view; 7: Hypopygium, ventral view. Scale bar: 5–7 = 0.1 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
